sns.boxplot(x='Price_range', y ='Aggregate_rating', data = df_rest, ax = ax,palette = sns.color_palette('magma', 5))
plt.subplots_adjust(wspace = 0.3, hspace = 0.4,)
plt.suptitle('Price Range & Rating Distribution', size = 30)
plt.show()
